{{Otheruses|Commerce Way}}
'''Commerce Way''' was the name of an avenue on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]], after the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] re-established the planet as the central world of the Republic. It was located in the [[Senate District/Legends|Senate District]], near the [[New Republic Obelisk]].

